      <p>
       Emls, t sm f s, r lk  plg. Thy sprd rpdly, nfct y ntl y’r cvrd n srs nd cn’t d nythng sfl, nd ltmtly fll th strts wth crpss.
      </p>
      <p>
       <span class="caps">
        OK,
       </span>
       myb mls rn’t
       <em>
        xctly
       </em>
       lk th plg.
      </p>
      <p>
       Bt thy cn tk p yr ntr dy f y lt thm. Entr th rt f brvty (nt t b cnfsd wth
       <a href="http://artofbrevity.com/">
        ths st
       </a>
       ).
      </p>
      <p>
       Mstr th rt f wrtng cncs mls, nd y cmmnct ssntl nfrmtn wtht tkng p mch tm – yrs r th rcpnts’ tm. Y ls ncrg th rspndr t b brf, wth yr wn brvty. And by lmntng chttr, y ls bcm  bttr wrtr.
      </p>
      <p>
       Sm tps fr wrtng brf mls:
       <span id="more-409">
       </span>
      </p>
      <ul>
       <li>
        <strong>
         Skp th sbjct ln
        </strong>
        . Cntrvrsl, s mny ppl blv th sbjct ln s ky fr smn scnnng thr nbx. Prsnlly, I lk t th sndr t dtrmn f I’m gng t rd th ml, nd I cn slly rd th 1st ln n Gml, jst frm th nbx. S th sbjct ln bcm rrlvnt. Jst skp strght t th mssg nd frgt mt dt. Th cntnt s th mt dt. If th rcpnt knws y, h’ll pn th ml. Nt: ths s ctlly cnsdrd rd by sm, s b wr f yr rcpnt’s xpcttns. Wth frnds, fmly nd cls cwrkrs, skppng th sbjct ln s fn. Wth mr frml mls, y’ll wnt  sbjct ln, nd y mght nt fllw vry sngl n f th fllwng rls.
       </li>
       <li>
        <strong>
         Kp t t  fw sntncs.
        </strong>
        I’v lng bn n dvct f th
        <a href="http://five.sentenc.es/">
         5 sntncs rl
        </a>
        nd n fct, f y cn kp t t 2-3 sntncs, tht’s vn bttr. Sttng  lmt frcs y t kp t brf – jst lk  hk.
       </li>
       <li>
        <strong>
         Skp th grtng.
        </strong>
        Sr, plt tqtt dctts y hv  grtng. Bt mstly w ml frnds r cwrkrs r fmly, nd rlly, d thy cr bt yr grtng? Thr tm s vlbl. Dv nt th mssg.
       </li>
       <li>
        <strong>
         Skp th sg.
        </strong>
        I ht lng sgntrs, spclly fr smn wh I tlk t rglrly. I lrdy knw ll yr nf – why kp sndng t? Jst sgn ff, s brfly s pssbl. My sg s slly: -l, bt f I rlly knw th prsn I’ll skp tht s wll.
       </li>
       <li>
        <strong>
         Nrrw th tpc.
        </strong>
        If y fnd yrslf ndng t wrt lng mls, t’s slly bcs y’r tryng t tlk bt t mny thngs. Ths tnds t ld t prblms – th rcpnt mght skp vr crtn prts, fr xmpl. Stck t n tpc fr nw, nd gt t th pnt.
       </li>
       <li>
        <strong>
         Edt.
        </strong>
        I knw, y wnt t wrt t nd snd t nd frgt t. Wll, tht’s rd, t th rcpnt. Y’r syng thy dn’t dsrv  gd ml. I’m nt syng y nd t spnd hrs mkng vry ml prfct, bt f y cn tk 10 scnds t g bck vr n ml, rmv nncssry sntncs nd wrds, y’ll b dng yr rcpnt (nd yrslf)  fvr.
       </li>
       <li>
        <strong>
         Cnsdr nt sndng.
        </strong>
        Smtms, n ml s nncssry. Bfr sndng, r vn bfr wrtng, cnsdr whthr thy rlly nd  “thnk y” r “gt t” r thr sch mssg. Smtms t’s fn, bt f th prsn snds y  “gt t’ ml, d y nd t rply bck “thnk y”? Jst mv n.
       </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
       If y knw ppl wh nd t rd ths pst, pls ml t t thm. Brfly.
      </p>
